    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedSettingsTitle">高级 USB 设置</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedSettingsIntro">此设置仅作用于当前选中的设备，并直接写入 QuickTime USB 分辨率请求。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedUsbResolution">USB 请求分辨率</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedUsbResolutionHelp">输入例如 1920×1080。应用后将忽略普通画面预设；关闭高级模式后恢复普通预设。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="WidthLabel">宽度</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="HeightLabel">高度</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DisableAdvancedMode">关闭高级模式</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedResolutionInvalid">请输入 16–8192 范围内的有效宽度和高度。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedModeEnabled">高级模式已开启</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="AdvancedModeDisabled">高级模式已关闭，恢复普通预设</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpAppleTitle">安装 Apple 设备支持</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpAppleBody">从 Microsoft Store 安装 Apple Devices，或安装桌面版 iTunes。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpTrustTitle">解锁并信任电脑</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpTrustBody">保持设备解锁，连接数据线，并在 iPhone 或 iPad 上选择“信任此电脑”。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpFilterTitle">安装当前设备的采集过滤驱动</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="DriverHelpFilterBody">点击主界面的安装按钮；授权完成后拔下并重新连接该设备。官方 Apple 驱动不会被替换。</system:String>
